Math Correlations Data

math_correlations.Rd

This data contains correlations on math ...

math_correlations

Format

A nested list with correlations and sample size:

math_correlations

A list of math correlations

sample_size

Study sample size

Examples

  math_correlations
#> $math_correlations
#> $math_correlations$Tracz.r
#>      ACH  PTE  GTE
#> ACH 1.00 0.14 0.62
#> PTE 0.14 1.00 0.22
#> GTE 0.62 0.22 1.00
#> 
#> $math_correlations$Sheft.r
#>       ACH   PTE  GTE
#> ACH  1.00 -0.01 0.19
#> PTE -0.01  1.00 0.27
#> GTE  0.19  0.27 1.00
#>

#> PTE 0.2437 1.0000 0.1768
#> GTE 0.1394 0.1768 1.0000

#>
